latestIgtvVideos.title: Night Owl Smart Safe
latestIgtvVideos.caption: Introducing Night Owl’s Wi-Fi Enabled Smart Safe. With Integrated Cloud Connectivity, you can easily connect to your Wi-Fi network and receive real-time alerts directly to your Smart Device. If your Safe has been opened or closed, you will be notified. If your Safe is moved, you will be notified. If the keypad is touched, you will be notified. If the Safe battery is low or your Wi-Fi connection is lost, you will be notified.

latestIgtvVideos.title: Night Owl's 5MP System with Human Detection & Facial Recognition
latestIgtvVideos.caption: Introducing Night Owl’s 5MP HD Wired CCTV Video Security System with Spotlights, Human Detection and Facial Recognition Technology. When the wired cameras sense human motion, a built-in spotlight will activate and you will instantly receive a Familiar or Unfamiliar Face Alert to your Smart Device. #smarthome #CCTV #surveillance #nightowl #safety #homesafety
